abstract: In the video, you can hear the disbelief and giddy joy in the voices of the fighters as they surround Qaddafi, who looks like a bloody rag doll but is still visibly alive. Some of them are shouting "God is great," but mostly the sound registers as a roar, a wordless expression of triumph.
